Package: shadowfetch-themes
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Shadowfetch Project <maintainers@shadowfetch.com>
Installed-Size: 17
Depends: plasma-workspace, breeze, papirus-icon-theme
Recommends: kde-style-breeze
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://shadowfetch.com/linux/
Description: Shadowfetch dark color scheme and look-and-feel
 Ships the Shadowfetch Dark KDE color scheme (signature violet accent
 on near-black background) and a minimal Plasma look-and-feel package
 (org.shadowfetch.dark) that bundles the scheme with sensible Plasma
 defaults: Breeze widgets, Papirus-Dark icons, breeze-dark plasma theme.
